WEBVTT

00:06:29.920 --> 00:06:31.776
for several days on end.

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:33.536
And if you watch the news,

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:39.480
you know that lots of communities
are having trouble with drinking water.

00:06:41.440 --> 00:06:43.176
I'm a scientist.

00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:45.296
I don't know if you could tell that.

00:06:45.320 --> 00:06:46.560
(Laughter)

00:06:49.560 --> 00:06:53.656
And I do solid science,
I publish my results,

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:58.080
my colleagues read them,
I get citations of my work.

00:06:58.840 --> 00:07:02.720
